- Shan.

11:41.570 --> 11:43.100
Kamu tenang sedikit, Shan.

11:44.870 --> 11:46.000
Ada apa?

11:46.150 --> 11:47.510
Shan, kamu tenanglah.

11:47.550 --> 11:49.310
Maafkan aku, Ibu.

11:49.360 --> 11:49.720
Ibu.

11:49.720 --> 11:50.650
Kamu bangunlah.

11:51.260 --> 11:52.040
Maafkan aku.

11:52.310 --> 11:52.790
Ibu.

11:52.910 --> 11:53.550
Maafkan aku.

11:53.550 --> 11:54.620
Ibu!

11:54.910 --> 11:55.360
Ibu!

11:55.910 --> 11:56.550
Ibu!

